    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>tomato paste</strong> and <strong>grated garlic</strong> in a bowl with your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong>, <strong>dried oregano</strong>, a pinch of <strong>sugar </strong>and 3 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[4 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[6 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold</strong> <strong>water</strong> – this is your <strong>tomato sauce</strong></p>",
