      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>potato wedges</strong> to a baking tray (or two!) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and put the tray[s] in the oven for 20-25 min or until golden and crisp</p><p>Meanwhile, line a separate baking tray (or two!) with <strong>non-stick baking paper</strong></p>",
